title: SET_TIMECYCLE_MODIFIER
content:
0x2C933ABF17A1DF410xA81F3638// SetTimecycleModifier
void SET_TIMECYCLE_MODIFIER(char* modifierName);Loads the specified timecycle modifier. Modifiers are defined separately in another file (e.g. "timecycle_mods_1.xml")
Parameters:
modifierName - The modifier to load (e.g. "V_FIB_IT3", "scanline_cam", etc.)
